=Description=

"Noosfero is an opensource web platform for social and solidarity economy networks with blog, e-Porfolios, CMS, RSS, thematic discussion, events agenda and collective inteligence for solidarity economy in the same system! Noosfero is being developed in Ruby programming language using the framework Rails. Therefore, it suports the databases PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQLite and others. Noosfero is free software, released under GNU Affero General Public License (AGPL), version 3."
(http://noosfero.org/Site/About) 


